review: I had cavity and tooth extraction and I was a bit skeptical and scared at first but Dr. manish kalra was very friendly, professional & at times funny too 😁. never felt as much pain as I anticipated. and I went to him by looking at good reviews and I felt that he lived upto the expectations. his wife performed the extraction and that was the part I was most scared about, she comforted me and explained about everything and told me that it was not a big deal and surprisingly it all went very smoothly.thank you so much to sir & ma'am for making this procedure smooth for me. ❤️🙏
